{"tid":2141079,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣教育部宣布（除了中國留學生）所有海外學生可以入境台灣隔離14天後回校","createTime":"2020-08-05T12:00:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T12:39:07.000Z","uid":22556,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4d47c636a99a5d4e437aae1ab4744cd75bd71c9d","tid":2141079,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T12:00:57.000Z","msg":"教育部於今（8/5）傍晚召開臨時記者會，教育部政務次長劉孟奇宣布，除了先前已開放的19國外，今天再宣布開放其他國家境外學位舊生返台，但仍獨缺陸生舊生。由於部分大學已收到解封公文是含陸生舊生，但劉孟奇突然接獲通知離開記者會，<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">約3分鐘後返回竟宣布排除陸生</span></span></strong>，並說要補充公文，讓學校一片譁然。也使得符合返台資格的逾萬名境外舊生砍半僅約5000人可來台，遭卡在境外的陸生約有5000人之多。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/life/20200805/YVVR2WUHCRW4CKOCOS5HELRNKQ/?utm_campaign=twad_social_apple.realtimenews&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flife%2F20200805%2FYVVR2WUHCRW4CKOCOS5HELRNKQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_apple.realtimenews%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2F85qU0izJB5q5dcgVJazxes%3D&h=e7240da9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flife%2F20200805%2FYVVR2WUHCRW4CKOCOS5HELRNKQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_apple.realtimenews%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=1bae18d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/life/20200805/YVVR2WUHCRW4CKOCOS5HELRNKQ/?utm_campaign=twad_social_apple.realtimenews&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"8b2a6b5414635f11a81ee81306f4ca0143c55680","tid":2141079,"uid":235015,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T12:02:52.000Z","msg":"奇怪，中國明明地大物博，點解仲要去小小台灣到讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成班肯撚定想做漢奸"},{"pid":"3591ed1ea3a9f3d2a677aafdb006299e1b9db859","tid":21